	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Recepi tuas, domine et frater colendissime, et quia in illis nihil est, ad quod respondere necesse sit, non exhibebo tibi ullam molestiam.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quae ab amicis hincinde scribuntur, tam sunt varia, ut, quid futurum sit, ignorem.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Pro certo asserunt artibus Caesaris effectum, ut <persName type="auto_name">Philippo</persName> desponsa sit <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18554">Maria</persName> atque ita tota <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Anglia</placeName> redacta in potestatem <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875" cert="high">Hispanorum</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si verum hoc est, non puto sine deo haec fieri; oportet enim horribiliter puniri per gentem truculentam et intollerabilem, qui tanta pertinatia et Christum abnegarunt et repulerunt.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">O domine, da servis tuis, ut constanter te confiteantur et colant religiose.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Domine, miserere nostri.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Aiunt quidam consilia captari a <placeName type="auto_name">Caesareanis</placeName> et papisticis mutua de continuando et redintegrando concilio <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1107" cert="high">Tridentino</placeName> et ideo cum <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Gallo</placeName> de pace concilianda tractari in hunc maxime finem, ut consentiat in concilium.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ubi enim conclusum fuerit unanimi monarcharum consensu, repetetur a <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l822" cert="high">Germania</placeName> et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l862" cert="high">Helvetia</placeName> subscriptio, aut bellum et proscriptio intendetur; ita vero mutuis armis confici posse creditur.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Haec est ars illius beluae.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Excisis autem aut sub iugum missis <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l822" cert="high">Germanis</placeName> et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l862" cert="high">Helvetiis</placeName> nullo negotio se <placeName type="citizen_name">Gallis</placeName> potiturum sperat Plus Oultre.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Haec fortasse abscondita sunt ab oculis <persName type="auto_name">Galli</persName>, et supplicium de illo et nobis sumi debet.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Oremus tamen misericordem dominum et hortemur omnes ad poenitentiam, si forte deus pacem det in diebus nostris.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed fiat domini voluntas.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale cum omnibus tuis.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tiguri</placeName> 9. ianuarii 1554.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Memor sis affinis mei.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Bullinger</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. <persName ref="p8055" cert="high">Ambrosio Blaurero</persName>, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l49" cert="high">Biennensis</placeName> ecclesiae fideli ministro, domino et fratri colendissimo suo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l49" cert="high">Byell</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
